comments:
They all start on S and end with G and S. After awhile, my brain started ignoring the first and last part of the word.

The hard part was reading the whole word, as it's not a very smooth word. But once I realized I can only focus on the middle part, it got easier.

The last test part was difficult because the word flash was very short. Sometimes I only saw one letter, sometimes I saw nothing, sometimes I read the whole word. I can't tell if speeds were different or if it's a brain thing.
